section.section:
The following are in the executive service, management service, or are special appointments in the State Personnel Management System:
each commissioner of the Commission;
the Executive Director;
the General Counsel and each assistant general counsel;
the Executive Secretary;
the commissioners' personal staff members;
the chief hearing examiner; and
each license hearing officer.

text.section:
The compensation of the following personnel shall be determined by the Commission and, if possible, in accordance with the State pay plan:
the Executive Director;
the General Counsel;
the special appointment attorneys in the office of General Counsel;
the Executive Secretary;
the chief hearing examiner;
each license hearing officer; and
all Commission personnel in positions in:
the management service; and
professional and technical classifications unique to the Commission.
